    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe or maybe Rolex. we need to define our \"ideal consumer\" profile really clearly for our investors. can you help me flesh out a detailed persona? i need to know their lifestyle, what they value, and also their typical ethnic and cultural background to make sure the brand feels \"authentic\" and high-status. what kind of person are we actually targeting here?",
