      "content": "For a luxury watch brand at that level, your ideal consumer is typically a well-established, high-net-worth individual, often from established families or successful global business elites. They value heritage, impeccable craftsmanship, and discreet exclusivity over flashy trends. While global, the most affluent segments often come from Western European, North American, or established East Asian business cultures, as these groups historically drive the highest purchasing power in this market.",
